# Submitting a form in ASP.NET Core

Here's the smallest razor snippet I could make for making, submitting and viewing a form in a razor page.

`
<form method="get">
    <div>
        <input type="text" name="searchGenre" value="" />
        <input type="Submit" value="Submit" /><br/>
    </div>
</form>

<h1>@Request.Query["searchGenre"]</h1>
`


